ollapse\">\n                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&amp;recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"main-image\">\n                        <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/73464/eawly5kq5xlIPCZtZLPASgIsTiXPHW-metadGVzdGluZ19raXRfc2NhbGVfdmFyLmpwZw==-.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table>\n                        <tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"><br></td><td class=\"attr-right\"><br></td></tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPLETE TESTING &amp; WEIGHING KIT - All-in-one set includes testing acid, neutralizing solution, testing stone, and a precision digital pocket scale for verifying both gold purity and weight with one convenient purchase.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ACCURATE ACID TESTING - Quickly determine karat authenticity by using the reliable scratch-and-test method; ideal for evaluating scrap gold, coins, and jewelry before buying, selling, or appraising.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HIGH PRECISION DIGITAL SCALE - Sensitive sensors deliver dependable measurements in grams, ounces, tola, carats, and grains, making it perfect for weighing precious metals and small valuables.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPACT PROFESSIONAL DESIGN - Portable scale features a clear backlit LCD display, tare function, counting capability, and auto shut-off, while durable squeeze bottles allow controlled, mess-free acid application.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">IDEAL FOR BUYERS, SELLERS &amp; COLLECTORS - Great for pawn shops, jewelry resellers, estate evaluations, and hobbyists who need a reliable way to test gold authenticity and confirm weight with confidence.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ToolTreaux Testing Kit with Acid Solution, Stone, Neutralizer and Digital Pocket Scale (7 Styles)</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">34.99</span></h2>\n                <p>Test, verify, and weigh with confidence using the complete ToolTreaux Acid Testing Kit with Digital Pocket Scale. This all-in-one gold verification set combines professional acid-testing solutions with a high-precision digital scale, giving you everything you need to determine both karat purity and weight in one convenient kit.\n\nComplete Testing &amp; Weighing System\n\nThis comprehensive kit includes:\n(1) 0.5oz Bottle Testing Acid\n(1) 0.5oz Bottle Neutralizing Solution\n(1) Gold Testing Stone\n(1) Portable Digital Pocket Scale with LCD Display\n\nThe testing acid is potent and effective, allowing for dozens of tests. Each solution comes housed in durable, shatter-resistant squeeze bottles for precise drop control and safer handling.\n\nThe included digital pocket scale features high-precision sensors capable of measuring in five units: grams (g), ounces (oz), tola (tl), carats (ct), and grains (gn) - making it ideal for weighing gold jewelry, scrap gold, bullion, coins, and other precious metals before or after testing.\n\nGOLD TESTING METHOD\n\nThis acid testing method is best used on raw or scrap gold due to the strength of the solution. When testing finished jewelry or delicate pieces, always scratch the item in an inconspicuous area to avoid visible damage.\n\nInstructions:\n\n-Scratch the gold item onto the testing stone, leaving a visible streak.\n-Apply a small drop of 10K testing solution onto the streak.\n-If the gold is 10K or higher, the streak will remain unchanged.\n-If the gold is lower than 10K, the streak will dissolve or fade.\n-Apply an equal amount of neutralizing solution after each test.\n-Thoroughly rinse and neutralize the testing stone before additional testing.\n\nHigh-Precision Digital Pocket Scale Features\n\nThe included compact scale adds professional-level accuracy to your gold evaluation process:\n-High-precision sensors for accurate measurement\n-Backlit LCD display for clear readings\n-Tare (zero-out) function for container weighing\n-Counting function for small items\n-One-minute automatic shut-off\n-Compact, portable design for bench-top or store use\n\nMaximum Capacities by Unit:\nGrams: 500g\nOunces: 17oz\nTola: 40tl\nCarats: 2500ct\nGrains: 7716gn\n\nWhether you are verifying scrap gold purchases, testing estate jewelry, or confirming bullion weight, this digital scale ensures precise measurements to complement your karat testing results.\n\nIdeal For:\n-Jewelry buyers &amp; resellers\n-Pawn shops\n-Coin and bullion collectors\n-Estate sale professionals\n-Precious metal hobbyists\n-Repair benches and appraisal work\n\nIMPORTANT SAFETY NOTICE\n\nTesting acids are corrosive and may cause burns. Always wear proper protective gloves and eye protection when handling. Avoid skin contact. Neutralize the testing acid after every use. Carefully read and follow all label instructions before use.\n\nWith both purity testing and precision weighing in one convenient kit, the ToolTreaux Gold Testing Kit with Digital Pocket Scale delivers accuracy, control, and professional-grade results every time.</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2026</p>\n            </div> <!-- /footer -->\n    \n        </div> <!-- /container -->\n        <div style=\"clear:both\">\n            &nbsp;<table></table>\n        </div>\n",
